&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-11437?focusedCommentId=15068627&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-15068627&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-11437?focusedCommentId=15068627&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-15068627&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15114123" author="lian cheng" created="Sun, 24 Jan 2016 02:19:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Quoted Davies&apos; offline comment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We always raise a exception in 1.4/1.5, different exception in 1.6/master, (the show() of 1.6.0 is weird, don&apos;t know why).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should raise a better exception when deserializing them in JVM (EvaluatePython.fromJava).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15114125" author="apachespark" created="Sun, 24 Jan 2016 02:27:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;liancheng&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
