&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/10886&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/10886&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15124528" author="hhadi" created="Sat, 30 Jan 2016 00:43:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am using the scala api and I do see the same issue: when the schema does not match the row a generic java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException exception is raised. will this PR solve the scala/java api too ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15124556" author="lian cheng" created="Sat, 30 Jan 2016 01:05:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, it should.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
